            <p>A leaked trailer for 007 First Light - the Bond origin game from Hitman developer <a href="https://www.eurogamer.net/companies/io-interactive">IO Interactive</a> - has shined a light on one the villains set to appear in the upcoming release. And, they are played by a name you will likely recognise, but perhaps not expect.</p>
<p><strong>Please be aware of potential 007 First Light spoilers below. </strong></p>
